    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, featuring a whisper-quiet engine and seamless shifting that reflects its meticulous upkeep. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as intended, offering a driving experience that is both refined and worry-free. This is a collector-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning buyer looking for a vehicle in top-tier condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
